      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl156_LabelType\">You have a special connection between you and Calistria that enhances your ability to achieve vengeance.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl156_LabelType\">Elf worshipper of Calistria</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl156_LabelType\">When a creature damages you with a weapon, on your next turn you gain a +1 trait bonus on weapon damage against that creature. If this creature is your ilduliel (see page 8), this bonus increases to +2.</span></p>",
